Contextual Automated 3D Analysis of Subcellular Organelles Adapted to High-Content Screening
Thierry Dorval, Arnaud Ogier, Auguste Genovesio, Hye Kuyon Lim, Do Yoon Kwon, Joo-Hyun Lee, Howard J. Worman, William Dauer and Regis Grailhe J Biomol Screen 2010 15: 847 originally published online 16 July 2010 DOI: 10.1177/1087057110374993 The online version of this article can be found at: http://jbx.sagepub.com/content/15/7/847

